data.title: Bermuda Optimist National & Open Championship Green Fleet Overall Results
data.meta_description: Bermuda Optimist National & Open Championship Green Fleet Overall Results - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The results are from a sailing regatta held on November 13, 2017. 10 boats completed the 12 races, with Maximilian Seuss from the USA finishing first overall with a net score of 19 points. Kipling Rossouw from Australia finished second with 33 points, and Jack Butterworth from Bermuda finished third with 63 points. The scoring system used is detailed in Appendix A.
